            <title>内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）</title>
            <link>https://lapin.ithome.com/html/digi/977236.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://lapin.ithome.com/html/digi/977236.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 14:08:46 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <h2>活动随时结束</h2><p>京东【宝威玛旗舰店】</p><p>宝威玛（BVGMAV）纯钛保温饭盒今日开启限时狂促，套装含钛筷勺：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>三层 2.5L 定价 759 元 → 折后 188 元</p></li><li><p>四层 2.7L 定价 799 元 → 折后 198 元</p></li></ul><p>内盒钛含量达 99.9%，另外官方支持 12 期免息 + 30 天免费试用：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>先领 5 折京东平台补贴券：<a href="https://coupon.m.jd.com/coupons/show.action?linkKey=AAROH_xIpeffAs_-naABEFoeRy23NJRwCWWU_d9sfWXOa6xDgedohm8zwaYwIJYVJDFZBqJMuGsUuaRYaY0vvCwuMptFuQ&amp;to=m.jd.com" target="_blank">点此领券</a></p></li></ul><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/9Gzn103" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/386234/35/21048/79083/6985be23F344d3c57/00833203205ba786.png" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">宝威玛 纯钛保温饭盒</span></span><span class="card-abstract">四层 2.7L 钛雅金</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 198 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 8 折券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/96z3X9w" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/386234/35/21048/79083/6985be23F344d3c57/00833203205ba786.png" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">宝威玛 纯钛保温饭盒</span></span><span class="card-abstract">三层 2.5L 钛雅金</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 188 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 8 折券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>另外可以咨询客服，目前纯钛饭盒下单晒单返现 20 元（一定要联系客服确认），折合仅需 168~178 元。</p><p>小伙伴们可全网比价后再下单，<strong>此款各平台日常大促价均在 400 元以上。</strong></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>小饭盒外盒是食品级 pp 材质的 → 外壳支持微波炉加热</p></li><li><p>小饭盒内胆是钛（含量达 99.9%）→ 不支持微波加热</p></li><li><p>保温桶内胆是 304 不锈钢</p></li></ul><p>这款整体重量不轻，整体做工非常扎实（碗筷盒外部会有些脏），不太适合给小学生带饭（可能拎不动），其他方面都算不错，上次下单的老哥们反馈很 OK。</p><p>加热的时候需取出纯钛内胆，用 PP 外盒加热，拆开也更方便清洗。</p><p>饭盒的 PP 外盒支持微波炉加热：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="661" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/e4487634-ff1a-46b1-9207-a4dbf0d7373f.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="584" /></p><h2>官方简介</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1074" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/7/bf30d84f-c780-4c00-99ba-a14a4178cde5.jpg" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="790" /><img height="896" src="https://img10.360buyimg.com/img/jfs/t1/417657/23/5520/77586/69d9ac6dF8b710f98/0083316380f362ca.jpg" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="790" /><img height="750" src="https://img10.360buyimg.com/img/jfs/t1/417155/13/7423/69603/69d9ac6dFec94f0f2/00833162eee3d922.jpg" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="790" /><img height="844" src="https://img10.360buyimg.com/img/jfs/t1/417119/32/7068/132755/69d9ac6cF9767a9e3/008331634cfee20f.jpg" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="790" /><img height="1126" src="https://img10.360buyimg.com/img/jfs/t1/418839/24/2457/62027/69d9ac61F59825307/008331646635d117.jpg" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="790" /><img height="1105" src="https://img10.360buyimg.com/img/jfs/t1/418978/19/1521/56010/69d9ac60Fdd620bc1/00833164513f56e6.jpg" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="790" /></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>先领 5 折京东平台补贴券：<a href="https://coupon.m.jd.com/coupons/show.action?linkKey=AAROH_xIpeffAs_-naABEFoeRy23NJRwCWWU_d9sfWXOa6xDgedohm8zwaYwIJYVJDFZBqJMuGsUuaRYaY0vvCwuMptFuQ&amp;to=m.jd.com" target="_blank">点此领券</a></p></li></ul><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/9DzNja3" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/386234/35/21048/79083/6985be23F344d3c57/00833203205ba786.png" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">宝威玛 纯钛保温饭盒</span></span><span class="card-abstract">四层 2.7L 钛雅金</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 198 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 8 折券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/9OzTwrv" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/386234/35/21048/79083/6985be23F344d3c57/00833203205ba786.png" title="内盒钛含量达 99.9%：宝威玛四层保温饭盒 799 → 198 元 12 期免息（含钛筷勺）" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">宝威玛 纯钛保温饭盒</span></span><span class="card-abstract">三层 2.5L 钛雅金</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 188 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 8 折券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p><div class="tagging1">【广告】</div>
